<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Auditoría de Embudo · PRB-2026 · Matix Media</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,700;9..144,900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.0/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root{
    /* Matix Media brand palette — muestreada del logo */
    --bg:#04050A;            /* Negro profundo del fondo del logo */
    --bg-2:#0B0C12;          /* Variante sutil para secciones */
    --panel:#10121A;         /* Paneles y tarjetas */
    --panel-2:#161823;       /* Hover / estado activo */
    --line:#1E202C;          /* Bordes principales */
    --line-2:#2A2C3A;        /* Bordes énfasis */
    --ink:#FDFCF7;           /* Blanco crema del interior del logo */
    --ink-dim:#A8A598;       /* Texto secundario */
    --ink-muted:#6B6A5E;     /* Texto terciario */
    --accent:#E8C046;        /* Oro — color primario de marca */
    --accent-2:#F5D066;      /* Oro claro para hover */
    --accent-deep:#B8942C;   /* Oro oscuro para gradientes */
    --green:#199477;         /* Verde teal del logo */
    --green-light:#2AAE8E;   /* Verde claro */
    --red:#CF343A;           /* Rojo del logo */
    --red-light:#E04A50;     /* Rojo claro */
    --amber:#E8C046;         /* Alias de accent (ámbar = oro de marca) */
    --blue:#199477;          /* Reemplazado por verde marca (no hay azul) */
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html,body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  body{
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 85% -10%, rgba(232,192,70,0.08), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 500px at 0% 100%, rgba(25,148,119,0.06), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(700px 400px at 50% 20%, rgba(207,52,58,0.03), transparent 60%),
      var(--bg);
    min-height:100vh;
  }
  .wrap{max-width:1320px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 28px 80px}
  /* HEADER */
  .head{
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom:30px;
    margin-bottom:40px;
    position:relative;
  }
  .head::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute;
    top:-32px;right:-28px;
    width:360px;height:360px;
    background-image:
      repeating-radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, transparent 0, transparent 18px, rgba(232,192,70,0.035) 19px, rgba(232,192,70,0.035) 20px);
    pointer-events:none;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, black 0%, transparent 70%);
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, black 0%, transparent 70%);
    z-index:0;
  }
  .head-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:30px;flex-wrap:wrap;position:relative;z-index:1}
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px}
  .brand-logo{
    width:72px;height:72px;
    border-radius:50%;
    display:block;
    flex-shrink:0;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(232,192,70,0.15),
      0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
      0 2px 6px rgba(232,192,70,0.12);
  }
  .brand-meta{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);font-weight:500}
  .brand-name{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-top:4px;color:var(--ink)}
  .brand-tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-top:2px}
  .date-picker{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px}
  .date-picker label{color:var(--ink-muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:9.5px}
  .date-picker input{background:transparent;border:0;color:var(--ink);font-family:inherit;font-size:11px;outline:0;width:115px}
  .date-picker input[type=date]::-webkit-calendar-picker-indicator{filter:invert(0.7) sepia(0.4) saturate(3) hue-rotate(10deg);cursor:pointer}
  h1{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:400;font-size:52px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1;margin:30px 0 8px}
  h1 em{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:var(--accent-2)}
  .subtitle{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim)}
  .period-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(216,165,87,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(216,165,87,0.25);color:var(--accent-2);padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-top:14px}
  .period-badge .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(216,165,87,0.2)}

  /* SECTION */
  section{margin-top:56px}
  .s-head{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:14px;margin-bottom:22px;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  .s-num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:0.15em}
  .s-title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:28px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;flex:1}
  .s-hint{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);font-style:italic}

  /* METRIC CARDS */
  .cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);gap:14px}
  .card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:18px 18px 20px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .card::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--accent),transparent);opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:var(--line-2);background:var(--panel-2)}
  .card:hover::before{opacity:1}
  .card.active{border-color:var(--accent);background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(216,165,87,0.08),var(--panel) 70%)}
  .card-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .card-value{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:400;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-0.025em;line-height:1}
  .card-sub{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);margin-top:8px;letter-spacing:0.02em}
  .card-sub.pos{color:var(--green)}
  .card-sub.neg{color:var(--red)}
  .card-sub.warn{color:var(--amber)}

  /* TABLE */
  .tbl-wrap{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px}
  th{background:var(--bg-2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-muted);text-align:left;padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;white-space:nowrap}
  th.num{text-align:right}
  th.sortable:hover{color:var(--accent)}
  th .arr{opacity:0.4;font-size:9px;margin-left:4px}
  th.sorted .arr{opacity:1;color:var(--accent)}
  td{padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12.5px}
  td.num{text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  td.name{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.005em}
  tr:last-child td{border-bottom:0}
  tr:hover td{background:rgba(216,165,87,0.03)}
  .bar-cell{position:relative}
  .bar-fill{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(216,165,87,0.18),rgba(216,165,87,0.05));border-right:2px solid var(--accent);pointer-events:none}
  .bar-cell span{position:relative;z-index:1}

  /* TABS for card-driven metric toggling */
  .card[data-metric]{user-select:none}

  /* FUNNEL */
  .funnel{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:28px}
  .funnel-stage{display:grid;grid-template-columns:180px 1fr 180px;align-items:center;gap:22px;padding:14px 0;position:relative}
  .funnel-stage + .funnel-stage{border-top:1px dashed var(--line)}
  .fs-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim)}
  .fs-label .fs-num{display:block;color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3px}
  .fs-bar-wrap{height:52px;background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
  .fs-bar{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent-deep) 0%,var(--accent) 60%,var(--accent-2) 100%);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#04050A;letter-spacing:-0.02em;transition:width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1);white-space:nowrap}
  .fs-meta{text-align:right;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-dim)}
  .fs-meta b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500}
  .fs-retention{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 0;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
  .fs-retention .ret-num{color:var(--green);font-weight:700}
  .fs-retention .ret-num.warn{color:var(--amber)}
  .fs-retention .ret-num.bad{color:var(--red)}
  .fs-retention svg{opacity:0.4}

  /* DIAGNOSIS CARD */
  .diag{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(208,90,74,0.08) 0%,var(--panel) 45%);border:1px solid var(--line);border-left:3px solid var(--red);border-radius:10px;padding:26px 28px;margin-top:24px}
  .diag.warn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(232,163,61,0.08) 0%,var(--panel) 45%);border-left-color:var(--amber)}
  .diag.ok{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(127,176,105,0.08) 0%,var(--panel) 45%);border-left-color:var(--green)}
  .diag-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .diag-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);font-weight:700}
  .diag.warn .diag-label{color:var(--amber)}
  .diag.ok .diag-label{color:var(--green)}
  .diag-stage{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-top:6px}
  .diag-drop{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;text-align:right;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-dim)}
  .diag-drop b{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:34px;font-weight:500;display:block;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:-0.02em}
  .diag.warn .diag-drop b{color:var(--amber)}
  .diag.ok .diag-drop b{color:var(--green)}
  .diag-problem{font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--ink-dim);margin:14px 0 18px;max-width:820px}
  .diag-problem b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500}
  .action-list{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:12px}
  .action-item{background:var(--bg-2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px}
  .action-item h4{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:8px}
  .action-item p{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);line-height:1.55}

  /* CHARTS */
  .chart-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
  .chart-card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:22px 24px}
  .chart-card.full{grid-column:1 / -1}
  .chart-title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:4px}
  .chart-sub{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--ink-muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px}
  .chart-host{position:relative;height:300px}

  /* NOTE banner for data limitation */
  .note{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(25,148,119,0.08),transparent);border:1px solid rgba(25,148,119,0.28);border-left:3px solid var(--green);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:18px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);line-height:1.6;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start}
  .note svg{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;color:var(--green)}
  .note b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500}

  /* SCALE RECOMMENDATIONS */
  .rec-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(340px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:6px}
  .rec{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:22px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .rec::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%}
  .rec.scale::before{background:var(--green)}
  .rec.keep::before{background:var(--amber)}
  .rec.pause::before{background:var(--red)}
  .rec-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .rec-tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px}
  .rec.scale .rec-tag{background:rgba(127,176,105,0.15);color:var(--green)}
  .rec.keep .rec-tag{background:rgba(232,163,61,0.15);color:var(--amber)}
  .rec.pause .rec-tag{background:rgba(208,90,74,0.15);color:var(--red)}
  .rec-camp{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-top:10px}
  .rec-reason{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-dim);line-height:1.6;margin-top:10px}
  .rec-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;margin-top:16px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px dashed var(--line)}
  .rec-stat-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-bottom:4px}
  .rec-stat-val{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.01em}

  /* FOOTER */
  footer{margin-top:70px;padding-top:26px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--ink-muted);text-transform:uppercase}

  @media (max-width:960px){
    h1{font-size:38px}
    .cards{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
    .chart-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .funnel-stage{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:8px}
    .fs-meta{text-align:left}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header class="head">
    <div class="head-top">
      <div class="brand">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Matix Media">
        <div>
          <div class="brand-meta">Matix Media</div>
          <div class="brand-name">Performance Audit</div>
          <div class="brand-tag">Cliente · PRB-2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center">
        <div class="date-picker">
          <label>Desde</label>
          <input type="date" id="date-from" value="2026-04-01">
        </div>
        <div class="date-picker">
          <label>Hasta</label>
          <input type="date" id="date-to" value="2026-04-17">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1>Auditoría de Embudo <em>— Google Ads</em></h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Diagnóstico clínico de fugas · Plan de escala y pausa</div>
    <div class="period-badge"><span class="dot"></span><span id="period-display">1 de abril de 2026 — 17 de abril de 2026 · 17 días</span></div>
  </header>

  <!-- 1. METRIC CARDS -->
  <section>
    <div class="s-head">
      <span class="s-num">01</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Métricas Principales</h2>
      <span class="s-hint">Clic para resaltar en las tablas</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cards" id="cards"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. SERIE POR CAMPAÑA (adaptado) -->
  <section>
    <div class="s-head">
      <span class="s-num">02</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Serie Interactiva — Clics · Conversiones · Costo</h2>
      <span class="s-hint">Ordena por cualquier columna</span>
    </div>
    <div class="note">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
      <div>
        <b>Nota sobre granularidad temporal:</b> el CSV de Google Ads proporcionado está agregado al período completo (17 días) sin columna de <code>Día</code>, <code>Semana</code> o <code>Mes</code>. Para obtener serie temporal real, exporta el reporte con la dimensión <b>Día</b> activa en el editor de columnas. Mientras tanto, adapto la serie a <b>vista por campaña</b> que sí permite comparación estructural.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tbl-wrap">
      <table id="tbl-series">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="sortable" data-sort="Campaña">Campaña <span class="arr">▲▼</span></th>
            <th class="sortable num" data-sort="Clics">Clics <span class="arr">▲▼</span></th>
            <th class="sortable num" data-sort="Conv">Conversiones <span class="arr">▲▼</span></th>
            <th class="sortable num" data-sort="Costo">Costo (COP) <span class="arr">▲▼</span></th>
            <th class="sortable num" data-sort="CPA">CPA <span class="arr">▲▼</span></th>
            <th class="sortable num" data-sort="ConvRate">% Conv. <span class="arr">▲▼</span></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. FUNNEL -->
  <section>
    <div class="s-head">
      <span class="s-num">03</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Visualización del Embudo Expandido</h2>
      <span class="s-hint">Adaptado a lead-gen (sin e-commerce)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="note">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
      <div>
        <b>Adaptación del embudo:</b> la cuenta es <b>lead-gen</b> (dental/medical), por lo que las etapas e-commerce (<i>View Content · Add to Cart · Initiate Checkout · Purchase</i>) no existen en el reporte. El embudo se construye con las etapas disponibles: <b>Impresiones → Clics → CTR → Conversiones → % Conversión</b>, donde cada conversión representa un lead capturado (formulario o WhatsApp).
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="funnel" id="funnel"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. MICRO-CONVERSIONS RETENTION TABLE -->
  <section>
    <div class="s-head">
      <span class="s-num">04</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Micro-Conversiones — Tasa de Retención</h2>
      <span class="s-hint">% de usuarios que avanzan de una etapa a la siguiente</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tbl-wrap">
      <table id="tbl-micro">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Transición</th>
            <th class="num">Valor Origen</th>
            <th class="num">Valor Destino</th>
            <th class="num">Retención</th>
            <th class="num">Caída</th>
            <th>Salud</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. CLINICAL DIAGNOSIS -->
  <section>
    <div class="s-head">
      <span class="s-num">05</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Diagnóstico Clínico de Fugas &amp; Plan de Acción</h2>
      <span class="s-hint">Protocolo específico por etapa</span>
    </div>
    <div id="diagnosis"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. SCATTER PLOTS -->
  <section>
    <div class="s-head">
      <span class="s-num">06</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Gráficos de Dispersión</h2>
      <span class="s-hint">Correlaciones estructurales</span>
    </div>
    <div class="note">
